Feature: User Valid Login
  As a registered user
  I want to sign in to the application
  So that I can access the user dashboard

  Background:
    Given the login page is displayed

  Scenario: Successful login with valid credentials
    When I enter the valid username 'user'
    And I enter the valid password 'pass'
    And I click the 'Sign In' button
    Then I should be able to observe the user dashboard
;
Feature: View Decision Tree Builder Creation Option
  As a signed-in user
  I want to see the option to create a new decision tree builder
  So that I can begin designing decision logic for the project

  Background:
    Given I am signed in
    And I can see my dashboard

  Scenario: Option to create a new decision tree builder is visible
    When I navigate to the Odontologist project
    And I open the Decision Tree Builders section
    Then I should see an option to create a new decision tree builder
;
Feature: Create a New Decision Tree Builder
  As a signed-in user
  I want to create a new decision tree builder
  So that it becomes part of the project

  Background:
    Given I am signed in
    And I see an option to create a new decision tree builder

  Scenario: Successfully creating a new decision tree builder
    When I select to create a new decision tree builder
    And I set the decision tree title to 'Custom-Decision-Tree'
    And I set the description to 'This is a custom decision tree'
    Then a message should appear indicating the decision tree builder has been created